\c 14
\s Abantu bavukela iN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Lenhlangano yonke yasiziphakamisa, yazwakalisa ilizwi layo\x + Gen. 45.2.\x*; abantu basebekhala inyembezi ngalobobusuku\x + 11.4.\x*.
\v 2 Bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebengunguna bemelene loMozisi loAroni\x + 14.27,29,36. Eks. 15.24; 16.2; 17.3. Nani 16.41. Josh. 9.18. Hlab. 106.25.\x*; lenhlangano yonke yathi kubo: Kungathi ngabe safela elizweni leGibhithe, kumbe kungathi ngabe safela kule inkangala\x + 14.27-29.\x*!
\v 3 Njalo kungani iN\nd kosi\nd* isilethe kulelilizwe ukuthi siwe ngenkemba? Omkethu labantwanyana bethu bazakuba yimpango. Bekungebe ngcono kithi ukubuyela eGibhithe yini?
\v 4 Basebesithi omunye komunye: Asimiseni inhloko\x + Neh. 9.17.\x*, sibuyele eGibhithe\x + Dute. 17.16. Seb. 7.39.\x*.
\v 5 UMozisi loAroni basebesithi mbo ngobuso babo phambi kwebandla lonke lenhlangano yabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 16.4,22.\x*.
\p
\v 6 UJoshuwa indodana kaNuni loKalebi indodana kaJefune ababengabalabo abahlola ilizwe, basebedabula izembatho zabo,
\v 7 bakhuluma kunhlangano yonke yabantwana bakoIsrayeli besithi: Ilizwe esadabula kulo ukuze silihlole yilizwe elihle kakhulukazi\x + 13.27. Dute. 1.25.\x*.
\v 8 Uba iN\nd kosi\nd* ithokoza ngathi, izasingenisa kulelilizwe\x + 2 Sam. 15.26; 22.20. 1 Kho. 10.9. Hlab. 18.19; 22.8. Isa. 62.4.\x*, isinike lona, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju\x + 13.27. Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\v 9 Kuphela lingayivukeli iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Josh. 22.16,18,19,29.\x*; futhi lina lingesabi abantu belizwe\x + Dute. 7.18; 20.3.\x*, ngoba bayikudla kwethu\x + 24.8.\x*. Umthunzi wabo usukile kubo; leN\nd kosi\nd* ilathi; lingabesabi\x + Gen. 48.21. Dute. 20.1,4; 31.6.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa inhlangano yonke yathi kabakhandwe ngamatshe\x + Eks. 17.4.\x*. Inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala ethenteni lenhlangano kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 16.7,10. Levi 9.23. Nani 16.19,42; 20.6.\x*.
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Koze kube nini lababantu bengidelela\x + 14.23; 16.30.\x*? Koze kube nini bengangikholwa, ngazo zonke izibonakaliso engizenze phakathi kwabo?\x + Dute. 1.32; 9.23. Hlab. 78.22,32; 106.24. Joha. 12.37. Heb. 3.18.\x*
\v 12 Ngizabatshaya ngomatshayabhuqe wesifo, ngibathathele ilifa\x + Eks. 15.9,24.\x*, ngikwenze ube yisizwe esikhulu lesilamandla kulabo\x + Eks. 32.10.\x*.
\p
\v 13 UMozisi wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Khona amaGibhithe azakuzwa; ngoba wenyuse lababantu phakathi kwawo ngamandla akho\x + Eks. 32.12. Dute. 9.26,27,28; 32.27. Hez. 20.9,14. Hlab. 106.23.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo azatshela abahlali balelilizwe. Bazwile ukuthi wena N\nd kosi\nd* uphakathi kwalababantu, ukuthi wena N\nd kosi\nd* ubonwa ubuso ngobuso\x + Eks. 15.14; Josh. 2.9,10; 5.1.\x*, lokuthi iyezi lakho lima phezu kwabo, uhamba phambi kwabo usensikeni yeyezi emini lensikeni yomlilo ebusuku\x + Eks. 13.21.\x*.
\v 15 Uba ubulala lababantu njengomuntu oyedwa, izizwe ezizwe ngendumela yakho zizakhuluma zisithi:
\v 16 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayingelakho ukungenisa lababantu elizweni eyabafungela lona, ngakho ibabulele enkangala\x + Dute. 9.28. Josh. 7.9.\x*.
\v 17 Khathesi-ke, ngiyancenga, kawabe makhulu amandla eNkosi yami, njengokutsho kwakho usithi:
\v 18 IN\nd kosi\nd* iyaphuza ukuthukuthela, njalo inkulu emuseni, ithethelela ububi leziphambeko, kodwa engayikumyekela lokumyekela \add olecala\x + Eks. 34.6,7. Hlab. 103.8; 145.8. Jona 4.2.\x*\add*, iphindisela ububi baboyise phezu kwabantwana kwesesithathu lesesine \add isizukulwana\x + Eks. 20.5.\x*\add*.
\v 19 Thethelela, ngiyancenga, ububi balababantu\x + Eks. 34.9.\x* njengobukhulu bomusa wakho\x + Hlab. 106.45.\x*, lanjengalokho ubathethelele lababantu kusukela eGibhithe kuze kube khathesi\x + Hlab. 78.38.\x*.
\s UNkulunkulu uthi uzatshaya abantwana bakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Sengibathethelele njengokwelizwi lakho\x + Hlab. 106.23. Jak. 5.16. 1 Joha. 5.16.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa isibili, \add njengalokhu\add* ngiphila, umhlaba wonke uzagcwala ngenkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 72.19.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba wonke amadoda abone inkazimulo yami lezibonakaliso zami engazenza eGibhithe lenkangala, langilingileyo\x + Dute. 1.35. Hlab. 95.11; 106.26. Heb. 3.17,18.\x* lezizikhathi ezilitshumi, kawezwanga ilizwi lami\x + Gen.\x*,
\v 23 isibili kabayikubona ilizwe engalifungela oyise; futhi kakho owalabo abangideleleyo ozalibona\x + 32.11. Hez. 20.15.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa inceku yami uKalebi\x + 13.6.\x*, ngoba omunye umoya ubulaye, wangilandela ngokupheleleyo; ngakho ngizamngenisa elizweni ayengene kilo; lenzalo yakhe izakudla ilifa lalo\x + 32.11,12. Dute. 1.36. Josh. 14.9.\x*.
\v 25 (AmaAmaleki\x + 14.43,45; 13.29.\x* lamaKhanani\x + 14.43,45; 13.29.\x* ahlala-ke esigodini.) Kusasa phendukani, lisuke liziyele enkangala ngendlela yoLwandle oluBomvu\x + Dute. 1.40.\x*.
\p
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni isithi:
\v 27 Koze kube nini \add ngila\add*linhlangano embi, engingungunelayo? Ngizwile ukungunguna kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli abangunguna ngakho bemelene lami\x + Eks. 16.7,12.\x*.
\v 28 Tshono kibo \add uthi\add*: Sibili \add njengoba\add* ngiphila\x + 14.21,23; 26.65.\x*, kutsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, njengalokhu likhulume endlebeni zami, ngizakwenza njalo kini\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 29 Izidumbu zenu zizawela enkangala le, labo bonke ababaliweyo benu, njengokwenani lonke lenu, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili langaphezulu, lina abangingunguneleyo\x + 1.45; 26.64. Dute. 1.35.\x*;
\v 30 sibili lina kaliyikungena elizweni engiliphakamisele isandla sami ukulihlalisa kulo, ngaphandle kukaKalebi indodana kaJefune loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + 14.6,38; 13.6.\x*.
\v 31 Kodwa abantwanyana benu elathi ngabo bazakuba yimpango, ngizabangenisa\x + 14.3. Dute. 1.39.\x*, bazalazi ilizwe elalilahlayo\x + Hlab. 106.24.\x*.
\v 32 Lina-ke, izidumbu zenu zizawela kulinkangala\x + 14.29,33. Heb. 3.17.\x*.
\v 33 Labantwana benu bazakuba ngabelusi enkangala\x + 32.13; Hlab. 107.40.\x* iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + Hlab. 95.10; Dute. 2.14.\x*, bathwale ukuphinga kwenu, izidumbu zenu zize ziphele enkangala\x + Hez. 23.35.\x*.
\v 34 Njengokwenani lezinsuku elahlola ngazo ilizwe\x + 13.25.\x*, insuku ezingamatshumi amane, usuku ngomnyaka\x + Hez. 4.6.\x*, usuku ngomnyaka, lizathwala ububi benu, iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + Levi 5.1.\x*, lazi ukufulathela kwami.
\v 35 Mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngikhulumile. Isibili ngizakwenza lokhu\x + 23.19.\x* kulinhlangano yonke embi ebuthene imelene lami; kulinkangala bazaphela, bafele khona\x + 14.27; 26.65. 1 Kor. 10.5.\x*.
\v 36 Njalo amadoda uMozisi awathumayo ukuhlola ilizwe, esephenduka, enza inhlangano yonke yamngungunela ngokuletha umbiko omubi mayelana lelizwe\x + 13.32.\x*,
\v 37 lamadoda aletha umbiko omubi ngelizwe afa ngenhlupheko phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Kor. 10.10. Heb. 3.10,17. Juda 1.5.\x*.
\v 38 Kodwa uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni loKalebi indodana kaJefune, kulawomadoda ayeyehlola ilizwe, asala ephila\x + 13.8,16.\x*.
\v 39 Njalo uMozisi wakhuluma la amazwi kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli; abantu basebelila kakhulu\x + Eks. 33.4.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli banqotshwa eHorma
\p
\v 40 Basebevuka ekuseni kakhulu, benyukela engqongeni yentaba, besithi: Khangelani silapha, sizakwenyukela endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* eyithembisileyo; ngoba sonile\x + Dute. 1.41.\x*.
\v 41 Kodwa uMozisi wathi: Kungani-ke liseqa umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*? Ngoba kakuyikuphumelela\x + 2 Lan. 24.20. Nani 14.25.\x*.
\v 42 Lingenyuki, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* kayikho phakathi kwenu, ukuze lingatshaywa phambi kwezitha zenu\x + Dute. 1.42.\x*.
\v 43 Ngoba amaAmaleki lamaKhanani alapho phambi kwenu; njalo lizakuwa ngenkemba, ngoba njengoba liphendukile ekulandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiyikuba lani\x + 14.25,45; 13.29.\x*.
\v 44 Kodwa ngokuziqhenya benyukela engqongeni yentaba\x + Dute. 1.43.\x*, kodwa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* loMozisi kawuphumanga phakathi kwenkamba\x + 1 Sam. 4.3.\x*.
\v 45 AmaAmaleki asesehla, lamaKhanani ahlala kulezozintaba, abatshaya\x + 14.43. Dute. 1.44.\x*, abahlakaza kwaze kwaba seHorma\x + 21.3; Hlu. 1.17.\x*.